On the show today:

America's international allies join our cause… by writing a strongly worded letter;

the America-hating right and Left unite to undermine President Trump yet again;

and California is spending all of its money on hospice fraud and mountain lion bridges.

Watch here: piped.video/watch?v=pTtbturj…

On the show today: 

A new Netflix documentary about the so-called "manosphere" is lighting up living rooms everywhere, and we discuss what it means;

we discuss the problem of toxic femininity;

and Joe Kent’s got some serious legal troubles.

Watch here: piped.video/watch?v=o99KEARB…

On the show today: 

Tucker Carlson reports that he’s being targeted by the CIA… but should we believe him?;

the Oscars were meh, as per usual; 

and we examine President Trump’s options in the Strait of Hormuz.

Watch here: piped.video/watch?v=U6_kYV8S…

On the show today:

We debunk the 4 big lies told by opponents of President Trump's highly successful Iran action; 

Zohran Mamdani continues to provide aid and comfort to jihad supporters in New York City; 

and James Talarico wins the hearts of those who think Christianity is all just a matter of manners.

Watch here: piped.video/watch?v=r9_grXFY…

On the show today:

ISIS-inspired terrorists try to bomb a rally outside New York City’s Gracie Mansion…and Zohran Mamdani blames white supremacists; 

Mehdi Hasan and Tucker Carlson spoon over their shared hatred for America and its intervention in Iran; 

and we discuss the duration of the oil shock roiling the markets.

Watch here: piped.video/watch?v=_62HQ9ex…

On the show today:

Trump fires Department of Homeland Security Secretary Kristi Noem… and Tucker Carlson for good measure;

Gavin Newsom has now fully succumbed to left-wing brain rot;

and we bring you the latest on America kicking the hell out of the Iranian regime.

Watch here: piped.video/watch?v=KhugND-J…

On the show today:

Cowards, liars and America-haters unite to try to undermine President Trump’s action against Iran;

we talk about whether the war is a "distraction" from domestic priorities;

and we bring you the state of play in the Middle East

Watch here: piped.video/watch?v=W27C-w8m…

